Author: -Macaronis-
Text: Really great! I'm happy you're getting better :D  I'm still not in that "weight is not important" mindset but I'm scared of getting underweight again. It takes a lot to overcome this so respect for that!

Author: princess-kitty-belle
Text: I am shocked and horrified at the news that I will feel better eating more.  But seriously, good for you. Life is so much better when your body is nourished. I hope this continues for you.
